#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.change_ip:1 of
msgid "Change the network address of the current target device."
msgstr "修改当前目标设备的网络地址。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.change_ip:3 of
msgid ""
"This instance method uses the IP currently configured on this object as "
"the target device IP, then delegates the network change to the shared "
"``CrackerManager`` instance. If the device is currently connected and the"
" IP change succeeds, the object updates its own target address and "
"reconnects when possible."
msgstr ""
"此方法使用对象中已配置的 IP 作为目标设备 IP，将网络变更委托给共享的 ``CrackerManager`` 实例。如果设备当前已连接且 IP"
" 修改成功，该对象会更新自身的目标地址并在可能时重新连接。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.change_ip:10
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.set_device_ip:12 of
msgid "New device IP address, or ``\"dhcp\"`` to enable DHCP."
msgstr "新的设备 IP 地址，或 ``\"dhcp\"`` 以启用 DHCP。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.change_ip:13 of
msgid ""
"Subnet mask or prefix length for a static IP change. If omitted, the "
"device's current mask is reused."
msgstr "静态 IP 变更时使用的子网掩码或前缀长度，省略时复用设备当前掩码。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.change_ip:17 of
msgid ""
"Default gateway for a static IP change. If omitted, the device's current "
"gateway is reused."
msgstr "静态 IP 变更时使用的默认网关，省略时复用设备当前网关。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.change_ip:20 of
msgid "``True`` if the device accepted the change request, otherwise ``False``."
msgstr "设备接受变更请求时返回 ``True``，否则返回 ``False``。"

