#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.set_address:1 of
msgid "Update the target cracker address stored in this instance."
msgstr "更新此实例中存储的目标 Cracker 地址。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.set_address:3 of
msgid ""
"This method updates the local target address metadata used by this object"
" and synchronizes the inner ``SSHCracker`` target IP settings. It does "
"not communicate with the device, so it does not modify the real device "
"network configuration."
msgstr "此方法更新对象使用的本地目标地址元数据，并同步内部 ``SSHCracker`` 目标 IP 设置。不与设备通信，不修改设备真实网络配置。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.set_address:9 of
msgid ""
"Device address as ``(ip, port)``, URI-like string, or ``None`` to clear "
"the current target."
msgstr "设备地址，格式为 ``(ip, port)``、URI 字符串，或 ``None`` 以清除当前目标。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.set_device_ip:1 of
msgid "Change the network address of a device identified by its current IP."
msgstr "通过当前 IP 识别设备并修改其网络地址。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.set_device_ip:3 of
msgid ""
"This class method reuses the shared ``CrackerManager`` instance and sends"
" a single IP change request to the target device. When ``mask`` and "
"``gateway`` are omitted the device-side manager will apply its own "
"defaults."
msgstr ""
"此类方法复用共享的 ``CrackerManager`` 实例，向目标设备发送一次 IP 变更请求。省略 ``mask`` 和 "
"``gateway`` 时，设备端管理器将使用自身默认值。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.set_device_ip:9 of
msgid "Current IP address of the target device."
msgstr "目标设备的当前 IP 地址。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.set_device_ip:15 of
msgid "Subnet mask. If omitted, the device-side manager handles it."
msgstr "子网掩码，省略时由设备端管理器处理。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.set_device_ip:18 of
msgid "Default gateway. If omitted, the device-side manager handles it."
msgstr "默认网关，省略时由设备端管理器处理。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.set_device_ip:21 of
msgid "Delay before the device applies the change."
msgstr "设备应用变更前的延迟时间。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.set_device_ip:24 of
msgid "Broadcast address cached on the shared manager."
msgstr "共享管理器上缓存的广播地址。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.set_device_ip:26 of
msgid "ACK information from the device, or ``None`` on timeout."
msgstr "来自设备的确认信息，超时时返回 ``None``。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.set_ip_port:1 of
msgid "Update the target cracker IP and port stored in this instance."
msgstr "更新此实例中存储的目标 Cracker IP 和端口。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_basic.CrackerBasic.set_ip_port:3 of
