msgid "Get the PS switch status."
msgstr "获取 PS 开关状态。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.get_switch_status_ps:3 of
msgid ""
"Status tuple ``(status, (sw1, sw2))``, where ``status`` is the protocol "
"status code and ``sw1`` / ``sw2`` are the two PS switch state bits (0 = "
"open, 1 = closed)."
msgstr ""
"状态元组 ``(status, (sw1, sw2))``，其中 ``status`` 为协议状态码，``sw1`` / ``sw2`` 为 PS"
" 开关的两个状态位（0 = 断开，1 = 闭合）。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.get_voltage_a0:1 of
msgid "Get the voltage at measurement point A0."
msgstr "获取测量点 A0 的电压。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.get_voltage_a0:3
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.get_voltage_a1:3 of
msgid "Device response status and measured voltage in Volts, or None on error."
msgstr "设备响应状态及测量电压（单位 V），出错时返回 None。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.get_voltage_a1:1 of
msgid "Get the voltage at measurement point A1."
msgstr "获取测量点 A1 的电压。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_led_content:1 of
msgid "Set the LED display content."
msgstr "设置 LED 显示内容。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_led_content:4 of
msgid "Content type: 0 for text, 1 for image."
msgstr "内容类型：0 为文本，1 为图片。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_led_content:7 of
msgid "X coordinate of the content in pixels."
msgstr "内容的 X 坐标（单位：像素）。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_led_content:10 of
msgid "Y coordinate of the content in pixels."
msgstr "内容的 Y 坐标（单位：像素）。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_led_content:13 of
msgid ""
"Content data: UTF-8 encoded string for text, or RGB888 byte array for "
"images."
msgstr "内容数据：文本为 UTF-8 编码字符串，图片为 RGB888 格式字节数组。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_led_content:16 of
msgid ""
"Width of the content in pixels. For text, this is the pixel width of the "
"content; for images, this is the image width."
msgstr "内容宽度（单位：像素）。文本为内容的像素宽度，图片为图片宽度。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_led_image:1 of
msgid "Set the LED display image."
msgstr "设置 LED 显示图片。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_led_image:4 of
msgid "Path to the image file; common formats such as PNG and JPEG are supported."
msgstr "图片文件路径，支持 PNG、JPEG 等常见格式。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_led_image:7 of
msgid "X coordinate of the image in pixels."
msgstr "图片的 X 坐标（单位：像素）。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_led_image:10 of
msgid "Y coordinate of the image in pixels."
msgstr "图片的 Y 坐标（单位：像素）。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_led_image:13 of
msgid ""
"Whether to force-resize the image to 64x64 pixels. True: always resize to"
" 64x64 regardless of original size. False: preserve the original image "
"dimensions."
msgstr "是否强制将图片缩放至 64x64 像素。True：无论原图大小统一缩放；False：保持原图尺寸。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_led_text:1 of
msgid ""
"Set the LED display text. Only ASCII characters are supported. Each "
"character is 5 pixels wide and 6 pixels tall with 1 pixel spacing. The "
"screen resolution is 64x64 pixels with the origin at the top-left corner;"
" x increases rightward and y increases downward."
msgstr ""
"设置 LED 显示文本，仅支持 ASCII 字符。字符宽 5 像素，高 6 像素，字符间距 1 像素。屏幕分辨率 64x64 "
"像素，原点在左上角，x 向右递增，y 向下递增。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_led_text:6 of
msgid "Text content to display."
msgstr "要显示的文本内容。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_led_text:9 of
msgid "X coordinate of the text in pixels."
msgstr "文本的 X 坐标（单位：像素）。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_led_text:12 of
msgid ""
"Y coordinate of the text baseline in pixels. Note that the coordinate "
"represents the baseline (bottom) of the text, so set y to 6 to display a "
"complete first line."
msgstr "文本基线的 Y 坐标（单位：像素）。注意该坐标表示文本底部，若要完整显示第一行文字，y 应设为 6（字符高度为 6）。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_led_text:16 of
msgid "Whether to automatically wrap text when it exceeds the screen width."
msgstr "是否在文本超出屏幕宽度时自动换行。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_pwm:1 of
msgid "Set the PWM output on pin GP29."
msgstr "设置 GP29 引脚的 PWM 输出。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_pwm:4 of
msgid "PWM frequency in Hz."
msgstr "PWM 频率，单位 Hz。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_pwm:7 of
msgid "PWM duty cycle as a fraction between 0 and 1."
msgstr "PWM 占空比，取值范围 0~1。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_arbitrary:1 of
msgid "Set the waveform generator output waveform."
msgstr "设置波形发生器的输出波形。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_arbitrary:4 of
msgid ""
"A sequence of voltage sample points for a single waveform period (unit: "
"Volts). Each element represents the output voltage of one discrete sample"
" point. The time interval per sample is 100 ns (corresponding to a 10 MHz"
" sample rate). Samples are output in array order; one array represents "
"one complete waveform period."
msgstr ""
"单周期波形的电压采样点序列（单位：V）。每个元素表示一个离散采样点的输出电压，采样间隔为 100 ns（对应 10 MHz "
"采样率），按数组顺序输出，一个数组表示一个完整周期。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_arbitrary:10 of
msgid ""
"Waveform clock divider (integer, default 1). Actual output frequency = "
"DAC sample rate / (len(wave) * wave_clk_div)."
msgstr "波形时钟分频系数（整数，默认 1）。实际输出频率 = DAC 采样率 / (len(wave) * wave_clk_div)。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_arbitrary:13
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_standard:33 of
msgid "Execution status code and device response data."
msgstr "执行状态码及设备响应数据。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_dc:1 of
#, fuzzy
msgid "Set DC voltage output."
msgstr "设置NUT时钟。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_dc:4 of
msgid ""
"Output DC voltage (Volts). Must be within the device's allowed output "
"range and must not be negative."
msgstr "输出直流电压（单位 V），必须在设备允许的输出范围内且不得为负值。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_dc:7
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_from_file:11
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_sawtooth:20
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_sine:17
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_square:19
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_triangle:15 of
msgid "Device response status and response data."
msgstr "设备响应状态及响应数据。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_from_file:1 of
msgid "Load waveform data from a file and set the output waveform."
msgstr "从文件加载波形数据并设置输出波形。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_from_file:3 of
msgid ""
"The file should contain a sequence of voltage sample points (unit: "
"Volts), supporting comma-separated or newline-separated numeric formats. "
"The maximum number of sample points is 2048."
msgstr "文件应包含电压采样点序列（单位：V），支持逗号分隔或逐行排列的数值格式，最多 2048 个采样点。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_from_file:8 of
msgid ""
"Path to a text file containing waveform data. Each numeric value in the "
"file represents a voltage sample point (unit: V)."
msgstr "包含波形数据的文本文件路径，文件中每个数值表示一个电压采样点（单位 V）。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_sawtooth:1 of
msgid "Set sawtooth wave output."
msgstr "设置锯齿波输出。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_sawtooth:4
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_square:4
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_triangle:4 of
msgid "Output frequency (Hz)."
msgstr "输出频率（单位 Hz）。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_sawtooth:7
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_sine:8
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_square:11
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_triangle:7 of
msgid "Peak-to-peak voltage (Volts). Default is 1.0."
msgstr "峰峰值电压（单位 V），默认 1.0。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_sawtooth:10 of
msgid ""
"Fraction of the period occupied by the rising edge (0–1). 1.0 = standard "
"sawtooth (slow rise, fast fall); 0.5 = symmetric triangle; near 0 = fast "
"rise, slow fall. Default is 1.0."
msgstr "上升沿占整个周期的比例（0~1）。1.0 = 标准锯齿波（慢上升快下降）；0.5 = 对称三角波；接近 0 = 快上升慢下降。默认 1.0。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_sawtooth:15
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_sine:11
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_square:14
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_triangle:10 of
msgid "Initial phase in radians. Default is 0.0."
msgstr "初始相位（单位 rad），默认 0.0。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_sawtooth:18
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_square:17
#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_triangle:13 of
msgid "DC offset voltage (Volts)."
msgstr "直流偏置电压（单位 V）。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_sine:1 of
msgid "Set sine wave output."
msgstr "设置正弦波输出。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_sine:4 of
msgid ""
"Output frequency (Hz). Accepts a numeric value or a string with unit "
"suffix, e.g. ``1e6``, ``\"1m\"``, ``\"1MHz\"``, ``\"10kHz\"``."
msgstr ""

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_sine:14 of
msgid ""
"DC offset voltage (Volts). If ``None``, automatically set to ``vpp / 2`` "
"to avoid negative voltage."
msgstr "直流偏置电压（单位 V）。若为 ``None``，自动设为 ``vpp / 2`` 以避免负电压。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_square:1 of
msgid "Set square wave output."
msgstr "设置方波输出。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_square:7 of
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Duty cycle (0–1). 0.5 means a standard 50% square wave; 0.2 means high "
"level occupies 20% of the period. Default is 0.5."
msgstr "占空比（0~1）。0.5 表示标准 50% 方波；0.2 表示高电平占 20% 周期。默认 0.5。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_standard:1 of
msgid "Set standard waveform output."
msgstr "设置标准波形输出。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_standard:3 of
msgid ""
"This function generates a single-period waveform dataset in software "
"according to the specified parameters, writes it into the device "
"arbitrary waveform buffer, and the DAC loops over it."
msgstr "此函数根据指定参数在软件中生成单周期波形数据，写入设备任意波形缓冲区，由 DAC 循环播放。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_standard:6 of
msgid ""
"Supported waveform types: ``\"dc\"`` (DC voltage), ``\"sine\"`` (sine "
"wave), ``\"square\"`` (square wave), ``\"triangle\"`` (triangle wave), "
"``\"sawtooth\"`` (sawtooth wave)."
msgstr ""

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_standard:10 of
msgid "Waveform type name (case-insensitive)."
msgstr "波形类型名称（大小写不敏感）。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_standard:13 of
msgid "Peak-to-peak voltage (Volts). For non-DC waveforms, amplitude = vpp / 2."
msgstr "峰峰值电压（单位 V）。对于非直流波形，振幅 = vpp / 2。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_standard:16 of
msgid ""
"Output frequency (Hz). May be omitted for ``\"dc\"``; required for all "
"others. Accepts a numeric value or a string with unit suffix (e.g. "
"``1e6``, ``\"1MHz\"``, ``\"100kHz\"``)."
msgstr ""

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_standard:20 of
msgid ""
"DC offset voltage (Volts). If ``None``, defaults to ``vpp / 2`` to keep "
"the waveform non-negative."
msgstr "直流偏置电压（单位 V）。若为 ``None``，默认设为 ``vpp / 2`` 以保证波形非负。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_standard:24 of
msgid ""
"Duty cycle or slope parameter between 0 and 1. For ``square``, this is "
"the fraction of the period at high level. For ``sawtooth``, this is the "
"fraction of the period occupied by the rising edge (near 1.0 means slow "
"rise and fast fall; 0.5 gives a symmetric triangle; near 0.0 means fast "
"rise and slow fall). Has no effect on ``sine`` or ``triangle``."
msgstr ""
"占空比或坡度参数（0~1）。对于 ``square``，为高电平占周期的比例；对于 ``sawtooth``，为上升沿占周期的比例（接近 1.0 "
"= 慢上升快下降；0.5 = 对称三角波；接近 0.0 = 快上升慢下降）。对 ``sine`` 和 ``triangle`` 无效。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_standard:31 of
msgid "Initial phase in radians (2π rad = one full period)."
msgstr "初始相位（单位 rad），2π rad = 一个完整周期。"

#: cracknuts.cracker.cracker_o1.CrackerO1.set_waveform_triangle:1 of
msgid "Set triangle wave output."
msgstr "设置三角波输出。"

